g-raman/uenroll.summary: Significant activities have been observed on the g-raman/uenroll repository, primarily focusing on UI/UX improvements, bug fixes, and feature enhancements. This includes the addition of a copy link button and the removal of unnecessary imports, as well as the rearrangement of section info and the open section results by default.

g-raman/scraper.summary: Moderate activities have been observed on the g-raman/scraper repository, with recent contributions focused on maintaining the repository's structure, including file formatting.

profile_summary: As a Full Stack Developer with expertise in TypeScript, Python, and JavaScript, I'm dedicated to delivering top-notch solutions across the tech spectrum. With a strong foundation in DevOps and proficiency in frameworks such as React, Angular, and Next.js, I stay at the forefront of innovation, continuously exploring new technologies, including AWS, Deno, and Supabase.
